e-Yves|last6=Boëlle|date=May 11, 2010|doi=10.1073/pnas.1000886107|url=http://www.pnas.org/content/107/19/8778.full|volume=107|issue=19|pages=8778–8781|accessdate=January 14, 2013|pmid=20421481|pmc=2889325}} * {{cite web|title=Epidemiology of the Russian flu, 1889-1890 |url=http://contagions.wordpress.com/2011/01/03/epidemiology-of-the-russian-flu-1889-1890 |date=January 3, 2011 |first=Michelle |last=Ziegler |website=Contagions: Thoughts on Historic Infectious Disease |accessdate=June 19, 2013 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6HYgpnY0A?url=http://contagions.wordpress.com/2011/01/03/epidemiology-of-the-russian-flu-1889-1890 |archivedate=June 22, 2013 |deadurl=no |df= }}
