The [[Bayer designation]] '''Tau Capricorni''' (τ Cap, τ Capricorni) is shared by two [[star system]]s, in the [[constellation]] [[Capricornus]]: * [[Tau1 Capricorni|τ¹ Capricorni]] * [[Tau2 Capricorni|τ² Capricorni]], being the brighter of the two, often simply called τ Capricorni They are separated by 0.50° on the sky.
